1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,175 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 9=

19
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:13,329
The traitor General Sun Beiming

20
00:01:13,330 --> 00:01:14,739
raised a private army,

21
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:16,290
held the imperial consort hostage,

22
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,609
and plotted regicide.

23
00:01:17,610 --> 00:01:19,129
His crimes are unforgivable.

24
00:01:19,130 --> 00:01:20,650
He deserved to die.

25
00:01:20,770 --> 00:01:22,819
Cavalry General Gu Bei

26
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,290
has shown great loyalty and valor.

27
00:01:24,330 --> 00:01:27,170
He is hereby promoted
to Commander of the Imperial Guards,

28
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,329
to defend and protect the capital.

29
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:32,450
Princess Hulv of the Plains
is permitted to remain in the capital

30
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:35,019
for her meritorious service.

31
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:36,700
That's all.

32
00:01:37,050 --> 00:01:39,530
- Wise judgment, Your Majesty.
- Wise judgment, Your Majesty.

33
00:01:39,770 --> 00:01:40,650
Your Majesty,

34
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:42,620
Sun Beiming deserved his fate,

35
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:44,930
but he was Your Majesty's
appointed prince consort.

36
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:46,819
As for his marriage
to Princess Xiao Ling...

37
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:49,849
Sun Beiming abducted the Consort and
tried to force the Princess into marriage.

38
00:01:49,850 --> 00:01:51,420
Naturally, the marriage doesn't count.

39
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:54,980
I shall find the Princess
a worthy husband.

40
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:57,450
Gu Bei,

41
00:01:57,610 --> 00:01:58,810
for your meritorious service,

42
00:01:59,020 --> 00:02:00,700
- I'll give you the Princess's hand...
-  No!

43
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:01,830
I won't allow it.

44
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,420
Outrageous!

45
00:02:05,610 --> 00:02:07,170
How dare you defy His Majesty?

46
00:02:07,690 --> 00:02:09,530
Such blatant disrespect to His Majesty.

47
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:12,130
As expected, a foreign woman
has treacherous intentions.

48
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:21,850
Official Li, don't exaggerate the issue.

49
00:02:23,050 --> 00:02:24,139
In my humble opinion,

50
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:26,529
a progressive nation like Jing

51
00:02:26,530 --> 00:02:30,020
shouldn't cling to arranged marriages.

52
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:32,060
Marriage

53
00:02:32,090 --> 00:02:34,690
should be a woman's own choice.

54
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:36,900
Official Gu,

55
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:38,579
a woman's marriage

56
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:41,340
has always been decided
by her parents and matchmakers.

57
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:42,769
Official Hu,

58
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:44,970
that's an outdated way of thinking.

59
00:02:45,490 --> 00:02:47,460
Women can hold up half the sky.

60
00:02:47,770 --> 00:02:49,370
We need

61
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:52,090
some awareness of women's rights.

62
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:53,530
Women's rights?

63
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,650
What's that?

64
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:57,370
It means

65
00:02:58,090 --> 00:03:00,220
women should enjoy

66
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:03,460
the same rights as men.

67
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:05,850
Preposterous!

68
00:03:05,930 --> 00:03:07,970
How can women be equal to men?

69
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:11,550
Your Majesty,

70
00:03:11,930 --> 00:03:12,910
I believe

71
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,329
Princess Xiao Ling

72
00:03:14,330 --> 00:03:15,810
should decide

73
00:03:15,930 --> 00:03:16,970
her own marriage.

74
00:03:18,050 --> 00:03:18,960
Very well.

75
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:20,650
That seems only right.

76
00:03:25,810 --> 00:03:27,380
Looking good.

77
00:03:29,140 --> 00:03:30,140
Keep it up.

78
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,090
Yes.

79
00:03:31,530 --> 00:03:32,760
Two more plates of meat, please.

80
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:33,950
Coming.

81
00:03:34,210 --> 00:03:34,739
Hulv!

82
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:35,740
Stop right there!

83
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,769
Why did you speak out in court?

84
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:41,780
What's my marriage to you?

85
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,019
If you've got nothing else,

86
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:45,089
quit bothering me.

87
00:03:45,090 --> 00:03:46,580
I'm going to buy groceries.

88
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,489
How insolent!

89
00:03:47,490 --> 00:03:49,820
Why didn't you kneel before me?

90
00:03:50,330 --> 00:03:51,739
So what if you're a princess?

91
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,999
I'm a princess too.

92
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,250
I don't see you kneeling to me.

93
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:58,710
What's going on between you and Gu Bei?

94
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:02,699
This is for you, Miss Hulv.

95
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,430
Please come visit anytime.

96
00:04:04,650 --> 00:04:06,550
The world doesn't belong only to men.

97
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:08,139
Women can wear armor too

98
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,310
and achieve greatness.

99
00:04:09,810 --> 00:04:12,430
You lost
because of your brains and skills,

100
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,710
not because of your gender.

101
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,819
We started out as friends.

102
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:21,910
But

103
00:04:22,940 --> 00:04:24,059
I like him.

104
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,640
I want to marry him.

105
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:26,520
You!

106
00:04:27,060 --> 00:04:28,579
Have you no shame?

107
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:30,849
How can you say that so openly?

108
00:04:30,850 --> 00:04:33,089
What's wrong with saying I like him?

109
00:04:33,090 --> 00:04:37,409
I like him!

110
00:04:37,410 --> 00:04:38,849
He's my prince consort!

111
00:04:38,850 --> 00:04:40,560
Stay away from him.

112
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:42,169
Your prince consort?

113
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:43,409
Did he agree to that?

114
00:04:43,410 --> 00:04:44,939
I can fight alongside him.

115
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:46,529
What can you do?

116
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:47,769
I have money.

117
00:04:47,770 --> 00:04:49,640
I have power.

118
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:52,590
I'm beautiful.

119
00:04:57,020 --> 00:04:59,019
When a steppe woman wants a man,

120
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:00,520
she gets him.

121
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:03,849
But if you can't bear to leave Gu Bei,

122
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:06,670
you can come to the plains
as our servant,

123
00:05:06,730 --> 00:05:09,529
tending horses and herding sheep.

124
00:05:09,530 --> 00:05:10,969
I'll fight you for this!

125
00:05:10,970 --> 00:05:13,590
You're unbelievably ignorant!

126
00:05:17,170 --> 00:05:18,270
Useless!

127
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:19,670
Ignorant!

128
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,309
Take this!

129
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:22,859
Come on!

130
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,400
You're so crude!

131
00:05:37,850 --> 00:05:39,089
I still have memorials to review.

132
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:40,699
Forget the memorials.

133
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:42,769
We just took down General Sun.

134
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:44,259
We've got to celebrate.

135
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:45,320
Hot pot!

136
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:47,270
Your Majesty.

137
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,670
Your Majesty.

138
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,379
Gu Bei!

139
00:05:58,380 --> 00:05:59,139
We beat General Sun.

140
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,259
Didn't I help?

141
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:01,440
Didn't I?

142
00:06:04,820 --> 00:06:05,710
Of course.

143
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:07,329
Without all of you,

144
00:06:07,330 --> 00:06:08,969
our plan would've never gone so smoothly.

145
00:06:08,970 --> 00:06:10,660
- Then be my prince consort!
- Then marry me!

146
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:13,169
I don't think that's a good idea.

147
00:06:13,170 --> 00:06:14,059
I'm still young.

148
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:16,209
It's too early to get married.

149
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,270
Try this.

150
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:18,649
Please.

151
00:06:18,650 --> 00:06:19,329
Marry me.

152
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:19,729
I...

153
00:06:19,730 --> 00:06:20,169
I...

154
00:06:20,170 --> 00:06:21,230
Marry me!

155
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,529
Let me say something.

156
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:23,570
- Let me speak.
- Marry me.

157
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:26,939
Now that we're all gathered here,

158
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:28,459
we've defeated the biggest villain.

159
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,259
So,

160
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:31,379
let's celebrate tonight.

161
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,329
Everyone,

162
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:33,409
drink till you drop.

163
00:06:33,410 --> 00:06:36,320
- Drink till you drop!
- Drink till you drop!

164
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,350
Eat this.

165
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:50,230
Try this.

166
00:07:32,260 --> 00:07:33,139
How much longer?

167
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:34,790
I need to get back to work.

168
00:07:45,410 --> 00:07:47,590
On his wedding day,

169
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:51,080
Sun Beiming thought he'd already won.

170
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,120
But why did he prepare explosives?

171
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,499
Come on.

172
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:56,679
The man's dead.

173
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,400
Why dwell on it?

174
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,649
That night,

175
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:03,939
there was another signal flare.

176
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:06,590
Someone had to be sending him a message.

177
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:09,910
I think

178
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,590
he had someone backing him.

179
00:08:14,290 --> 00:08:15,880
Drink while you can,

180
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:17,790
live for today.

181
00:08:18,210 --> 00:08:19,910
Enjoy today's blessings

182
00:08:20,650 --> 00:08:22,910
while they last.

183
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,880
Tomorrow's problems

184
00:08:25,060 --> 00:08:26,230
can wait till tomorrow.

185
00:08:32,410 --> 00:08:34,240
Until we find the mastermind,

186
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:36,070
we'll never know peace.

187
00:08:36,690 --> 00:08:38,480
We'll always be on edge.

188
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,190
I think Xiaoyao Pavilion

189
00:08:40,530 --> 00:08:41,950
needs an upgrade.

190
00:08:43,810 --> 00:08:46,240
Great minds think alike.

191
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:51,550
I'm planning

192
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:53,360
to install surveillance.

193
00:08:55,530 --> 00:08:56,720
Surveillance?

194
00:09:14,050 --> 00:09:15,400
No way.

195
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:16,880
This...

196
00:09:17,170 --> 00:09:19,169
Isn't this
"The Night Revels of Han Xizai"?

197
00:09:19,170 --> 00:09:19,899
Bei,

198
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:21,190
you're a genius.

199
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,619
I don't know

200
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,619
whoever that Han is.

201
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,880
Those two work as a pair.

202
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:28,339
One sketches everything that happens,

203
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:28,899
and the other

204
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,529
records

205
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:31,670
every word.

206
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:32,569
From then on,

207
00:09:32,570 --> 00:09:34,859
we can monitor the officials' every move

208
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:38,480
and expose the mastermind.

209
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:50,449
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

210
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:52,829
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

211
00:09:52,830 --> 00:09:58,269
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

212
00:09:58,270 --> 00:10:02,649
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

213
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:05,059
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

214
00:10:05,060 --> 00:10:07,599
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

215
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:13,269
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

216
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:18,830
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

217
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,180
♪Funny moments never stop♪

218
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,990
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

219
00:10:28,210 --> 00:10:32,359
♪Yet through every up and down♪

220
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,330
♪We create miracles♪

221
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:37,090
♪From naive youths♪

222
00:10:37,350 --> 00:10:39,829
♪To legendary heroes♪

223
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,779
♪This journey♪

224
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:45,789
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

225
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:48,340
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

226
00:10:50,810 --> 00:10:53,680
♪Let's create♪

227
00:10:55,720 --> 00:11:03,640
♪A legend of our own♪
